React + React Hooks
React Context API -> REDUX Pattern
React Flip Move
Material UI
Flexbox
Firebase's Firestore realtime DB
Firebase Hosting
Firebase Google Authentication (FULL LOGIN!)

Dependencies:
  --> material ui
    npm i @material-ui/core

  --> material ui icons
    npm i @material-ui/icons

  --> react-flip-move
    npm i react-flip-move ---> import forwardRef

  --> react icons
    npm i react-icons

  --> facebook embed (iframe)

  -> setting up firebase
    npm install -g firebase-tools
    npm i firebase

    in the src folder, create firebase.js
      1- import firebase from 'firebase'
      2- the congif from firebase console
      3- write these 3 lines:
        const firebaseApp = firebase.initializeApp(firebaseConfig)
        const db = firebaseApp.firestore()
        export default db

  --> deployment with firebase
    firebase login
    firebase init
    firebase deploy